radiographic_examinations.findings: Thickening of the lower portion of the sigmoid colon, collection of air and fluid surrounding the uterus, dependent collection measures 6.4 x 1.9 cm, contiguous collection measures 4.7 x 2.0 cm. No active extravasation of intraluminal contrast, normal imaged small bowel and proximal large bowel, normal rectum, no pathologic adenopathy.
